<h2> This is a profile page for <%=@mood.name%>  </h2>
<h3> <%=@mood.name%>  is feeling like a <%=@mood.mood%> </h3>

<h3>If <%=@mood.name%>'s mood has changed use the form below to update it.</h3>


<form name="input" action="/updatemood/<%=@mood.id%>">
How are you feeling on the scale of 1-10: 
  <input type="string" name="name" placeholder="Type your name here" value="<%=@mood.name%>">
   <input type="integer" name="mood" placeholder="1-10 only please" value="<%=@mood.mood%>">
<input type="submit" value="Submit">
</form>
<h3><%=@mood.name=%>'s id is <%=@mood.id%>. Enter it below to destroy <%=@mood.name=%>'s data</h3>
 <form name="input" action="/destroy">
 <input type="integer" name="id" placeholder="Enter the profile ID to destroy it">
<input type="submit" value="Destroy">
</form>
